## PATCH /api/users/me

Scenario 5. ACC-011: a Customer can update their own profile — name only
(email is the account's unique identifier and isn't part of this rule;
changing it is new scope, not built here).

Request:
```json
PATCH /api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer <jwt for Alice>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Alice N. Nguyen"
}
```

Response — 200 OK:
```json
{
  "id": "aaaaaaaa-aaaa-4aaa-8aaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa",
  "email": "alice.nguyen@example.test",
  "fullName": "Alice N. Nguyen",
  "role": "CUSTOMER",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "updatedAt": "2026-07-13T09:15:00Z"
}
```

