## Regression check against Phase 1

- POST /api/auth/register and POST /api/auth/login are unchanged — no
  route, request, or response shape here touches them.
- A newly Deactivated account (scenario 7) must now fail login with the
  same 401 INVALID_CREDENTIALS body from Phase 1 (ACC-007 folded into
  ACC-005's identical-error rule) — verify this explicitly, since it's the
  first place these two phases actually interact.
